<div class="page_body">
<div class="log">
Validates&nbsp;the&nbsp;set&nbsp;channel&nbsp;layout&nbsp;as&nbsp;well&nbsp;as&nbsp;verifies&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;received<br/>
layout&nbsp;to&nbsp;the&nbsp;function&nbsp;matches&nbsp;the&nbsp;reference&nbsp;layout,&nbsp;so&nbsp;that&nbsp;it&nbsp;matches<br/>
the&nbsp;implemented&nbsp;re-ordering&nbsp;logic.<br/>
<br/>
Fixes&nbsp;#8845<br/>
<br/>
</div>
